channel.title: Need Range Guild Target Practice Script (willing to pay)
channel.description: The mini game in the range guild is completely repetetive, and should be easy to make a script for. If anyone would be willing to make a script for me that worked, i would happily pay them for it. I can explain exactly how the training works, and the series of repetitive clicks, as i have performed them thousands of times with my own hand. So far its gotten my main character to lvl 86 ranged, but i would like a program which i could train a pure with. Let me know if you can write this script, or if there already is one (i haven't found one). Remember, if you can get me a script that works, i will pay for it.
